{"tid":1635551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先同個淺黃老母傾計唔夠講","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:33:42.000Z","uid":29010,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8aa6471c9f7a14c138d87d9772d62fe91f0fcb2f","tid":1635551,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"頭先同個淺黃老母傾計 叫我地唔好再裝修<br />\n原因類似就係開始影響生活個啲on9野<br />\n當然我心入面都係覺得搞革命都仲要理民生係on9<br />\n但其中一句佢講到好多淺黃嘅uncle auntie平時捐好多錢比我地 但宜家都開始有微言(因為搞到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n佢有同事搭左幾日的士返工 同埋開始公司要交人<br />\n個感覺就係第一日塞機場係好好反應 但第二日就會有反彈<br />\n雖然係好on9 但我都好驚淺黃會割席 大家討論下文宣或者日後方向應該點"},{"pid":"ff1b01238754a64c94d200d41c5645f7fb6b590e","tid":1635551,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd88ad5777a672cb380934bf14b8f163007bc233","tid":1635551,"uid":29010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ad5230eccaa261eae9fd9444aae0ca5f41345a8","tid":1635551,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:09:51.000Z","msg":"就算佢割你唔等如佢支持政府<br />\n而且政府無論有冇人支持做事手法都係咁，多十萬少十萬佢都係玩緊急法"},{"pid":"809286931d4e45608539bc0dd3a2247fc3ab70e9","tid":1635551,"uid":91437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c206b0c3ea8ad21956afe2e1f1d27e60294ded2d","tid":1635551,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"文宣將個波推俾港鐵"},{"pid":"6c377e820b15976310c5a9a80b4d9865efd72ae0","tid":1635551,"uid":323797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:13:47.000Z","msg":"新口號：和勇相連 永不割蓆！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634504\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634504</a><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打絲打幫幫手討論下要唔要新口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.c